# Local-only research artifacts — must never ship to Vercel (the top-level data/ is ~1.4GB of
# backtest CSVs that blow past the 250MB function limit). The LEADING SLASH anchors to the project
# root, so this excludes the root data/ WITHOUT matching src/data/ (which holds build-time JSON the
# app imports, e.g. fund-snapshot.json). An unanchored "data/" matches src/data/ too and breaks the build.
/data/
/reports/
